reviews.review_text:
My 1st Show! Hampton Coliseum - What a cool place to see my first show!  The crowd was jazzed and I was in awe.  Stranger was fun and I really was a stranger in a strange land!  "You know its gonna get stranger, so let's go!"  Healey really let it loose with the reverb during the playout.

It was during Cold, Rain & Snow that I started to really get it.  When Jerry and boys belted out the first chorus, something clicked and I knew that I would be back for more.  There really is nothing like a Grateful Dead concert!

Nice audience recording, it has a good feeling.  A good show, though I'm not crazy about the after drums playlist.
